{
  "stem": "3638.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was-- and I never went, since then, because I was scared that he would be there, and he would recognize me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the only accident which I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How old were you with this incident?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about 15, maybe, 15 or 15 and 1/2, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was illegal to get in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was illegal to smuggle the food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, I did a few times, and once I was caught, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wasn't caught by the German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was caught by the Polish policeman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But because-- I believe, because I didn't went as far as took off my trousers, because if I would have took my trousers, they knew that I was circumcised.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Polish people were not circumcised before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I didn't went this far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, look, I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I told him the whole story, and I plead with him, and so he, he let me out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He let me have the bread, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is the only story which I didn't tell you, but when we came to it, I must tell you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a kitchen where they used to get-- everybody used to get soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The soup was quite [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But besides, there was some shops in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could obtain food and other things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, so a few businesses were--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Legally, yes, because it was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They smuggled, probably.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had some of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't, I wasn't that kind of-- but I know one thing, that you could get it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to have money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With Polish Zloty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Proper Polish currency, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this currency could be converted from gold, from gold.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
